          <h6 style="font-family:var(--tf-font-mono);font-size:0.8rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--tf-text);margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Punctuality</h6>
          <p style="font-size:0.7rem;color:var(--tf-text-muted);margin:0;">Login time vs shift start, average delay, and punctuality scores</p>
